original: Öberg, Carl-Oscar, tandläkare, Vänersborg, f. 11/6/Ö2 i Sthlm av C. N. Öberg o. Alma Nöjd. G. 26 m. Svea Wahlin. Barn: Ingrid f. 27, Margareta 29’, Barbro 30. — Stud:ex. v. södra latin i Sthlm 20, tandl :kand. 21, tandläk. 23. Vik. i Skara o. Mariestad 23, praktik i Bengtsfors 24-25, i Trollhättan 25-31 o. i Vänersb. sed. 31. Sekr. i Odont. fören. 22-23. Ordf. i Västgöta-Dals tandl :fören. o. Vänersb. tenniskl.
translated: Öberg, Carl-Oscar, dentist, Vänersborg, b. 11/6/1902 in Stockholm to C. N. Öberg and Alma Nöjd. Married on the 26th with Svea Wahlin. Children: Ingrid b. 1927, Margareta b. 1929, Barbro b. 1930. — Graduated from Södra Latin in Stockholm in 1920, dental student in 1921, dentist in 1923. Acting in Skara and Mariestad in 1923, practice in Bengtsfors from 1924 to 1925, in Trollhättan from 1925 to 1931, and in Vänersborg since 1931. Secretary of the Odontological Association from 1922 to 1923. President of the Västgöta-Dals Dental Association and Vänersborg Tennis Club.
